- ตั้ง `revalidate = 86400` (อัปเดตทุก 24 ชม.)

**Collections ที่จะดึง:**
| Collection | URL Pattern | Priority |
|---|---|---|
| `pages` | `/{slug}` | 0.8 |
| `posts` | `/blog/{slug}` | 0.6 |
| `intertours` | `/intertours/{slug}` | 0.9 |
| `inbound-tours` | `/inbound-tours/{slug}` | 0.9 |
| `program-tours` | `/intertours/{countrySlug}/{productCode}` | 1.0 |
| `custom-landing-pages` | `/custom-landingpage/{slug}` | 0.7 |

